        <briefdescription>
<para>Create a 1-D FFT instance. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Allocates one CF64 and one CF32 pocketfft plan for length <computeroutput>n</computeroutput>. nthreads is accepted for API compatibility but ignored.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>n</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Transform length in samples. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>sign</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>-1 for forward DFT, +1 for inverse. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>nthreads</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Ignored (pocketfft is single-threaded). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Heap-allocated state, or NULL on allocation failure. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
