    <briefdescription>
<para>Per-instance 1-D FFT using pocketfft directly. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Holds two pocketfft plans — one for CF64, one for CF32 — allocated at create time for the requested transform length and sign. nthreads is accepted for API compatibility but ignored; pocketfft is single-threaded.</para>
